    %% Simplified summarize flow
    Upstream[🔀 Upstream Workflow<br/>SQL Execution / Planning] --> SumNode[🧠 summarize_node]
    SumNode --> Extract[🧩 Minimal context extraction]
    Extract --> Agent[📝 ResultSummarizeAgent]
    Agent --> Summary[📄 Final markdown summary]

    %% Parallel enrichments
    SumNode --> Charts[📊 Chart generation]
    SumNode --> Tables[📥 Table downloads]
    SumNode --> SQL[📎 SQL / explanation accordions]
    SumNode --> Code[🔎 Code enrichment]

    Charts --> Summary
    Tables --> Summary
    SQL --> Summary
    Code --> Summary

    Summary --> Frontend[🖥️ Frontend stream renderer]
    Frontend --> User[👤 User]

